'''黑格斯敦'''（{{lang en|'''Hagerstown'''}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|h|eɪ|ɡ|ər|z|t|aʊ|n}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/Hagerstown |title=Hagerstown - Definitions from Dictionary.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2013-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217040017/http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/Hagerstown |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是[[美國|美國]][[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]][[華盛頓縣_(馬里蘭州)|華盛頓縣]]的縣治{{GR|6}}，亦是馬里蘭州西部最大城市。<ref name="Hag2">[http://www.mdoe.org/hagerstown.html Hagerstown, Maryland] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mdoe.org/hagerstown.html |date=20090113183356 }}, mdoe.org Maryland Online Encyclopedia. Retrieved 15 September 2008.</ref>根據[[美國2010年人口普查|2010年人口普查]]，本城共有人口39,662人，而黑格斯敦-馬丁斯都會區則共有人口269,140人。<ref>[http://www2.census.gov/census_2010/01-Redistricting_File--PL_94-171/California/ "2010 Census P.L. 94-171 Summary File Data"] {{Wayback|url=http://www2.census.gov/census_2010/01-Redistricting_File--PL_94-171/California/ |date=20130807061126 }}. United States Census Bureau.</ref>黑格斯敦是馬里蘭州第六大城市。<ref>[http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/GCTTable?_bm=y&-geo_id=04000US24&-_box_head_nbr=GCT-T1-R&-ds_name=PEP_2006_EST&-_lang=en&-format=ST-9S&-_sse=on Maryland by Place - GCT-T1-R. Population Estimates (geographies ranked by estimate)] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20200212034957/http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/GCTTable?_bm=y&-geo_id=04000US24&-_box_head_nbr=GCT-T1-R&-ds_name=PEP_2006_EST&-_lang=en&-format=ST-9S&-_sse=on |date=2020-02-12 }}, U.S. Census Bureau, 2006. Retrieved 2007.</ref>黑格斯敦-馬丁斯都會區是馬里蘭州發展速度最快的都會區。<ref name="Hag1">[http://www.census.gov/popest/metro/tables/2008/CBSA-EST2008-07.csv Table 7. Cumulative Estimates of Population Change for Metropolitan Statistical Areas and Rankings: April 1, 2000 to July 1, 2008] {{Wayback|url=http://www.census.gov/popest/metro/tables/2008/CBSA-EST2008-07.csv |date=20110604185735 }}, Census Bureau 2009. Retrieved 26 April 2009.</ref>

黑格斯敦是一個交通中心。81號和70號州際公路、CSX鐵路、諾福克南方鐵路、溫徹斯特和西部鐵路、以及黑格斯敦地區機場使本城成為一個交通中心。黑格斯敦亦是一個主要的商業和工業中心，因此本城的綽號為“中心城市”（Hub City）。<ref name="Hag2" />

==文化==
===古蹟===
黑格斯敦位於西馬里蘭州的中央，其歷史古蹟不少與[[美國內戰|美國內戰]]有關。美國內戰其中一個最激烈的內戰發生於[[安提耶坦國家戰場|安提耶坦國家戰場]]，而該戰場則位於黑格斯敦附近。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nps.gov/anti/ |title=NPS : official '''Antietam National Battlefield''' website |accessdate=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2010-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101106002007/http://www.nps.gov/anti |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[南山之役|南山之役]]發生地[[南山國家戰場|南山國家戰場]] 亦位於黑格斯敦附近。[[腓特烈堡州立公園|腓特烈堡州立公園]]擁有一個曾於[[法國－印第安人戰爭|法國－印第安人戰爭]]中使用的堡壘。<ref name="nrhpinv1">{{cite web|url=http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Text/73000939.pdf|title=National Register of Historic Places Inventory Nomination: Fort Frederick|last=Snell|first=Charles W.|date=January 23, 1973|publisher=National Park Service|accessdate=2009-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110527125146/http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Text/73000939.pdf|archive-date=2011-05-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[華盛頓紀念碑州立公園|華盛頓紀念碑州立公園]]更是美國首個為美國開國元勛[[喬治·華盛頓|喬治·華盛頓]]而設的紀念碑。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dnr.state.md.us/publiclands/washmonhistory.html |title=Washington Monument history |accessdate=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2008-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081026033848/http://www.dnr.state.md.us/publiclands/washmonhistory.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>黑格斯敦亦擁有不少列入[[國家史蹟名錄|國家史蹟名錄]]的建築物。<ref>"[http://nrhp.focus.nps.gov/natreg/docs/All_Data.html National Register Information System] {{Wayback|url=http://nrhp.focus.nps.gov/natreg/docs/All_Data.html |date=20101204052104 }}". National Register of Historic Places. National Park Service. 2008-04-15.</ref>

===公園和博物館===
[[File:Hagerstown_City_Park_Lake_and_Wash_Co_Mus_Fine_Arts.JPG|thumb]]
[[Image:Hagerstown_maryland_270492672.jpg|thumb]]
黑格斯敦擁有很多公園，其中包括黑格斯敦市公園。華盛頓縣美術館、萬勝藝術畫廊、馬里蘭州西部202機車博物館、以及海格大廈博物館皆位於黑格斯敦市公園內。<ref name="Hag2" />在合園外，[[黑格斯敦圓屋博物館|黑格斯敦圓屋博物館]]展示關於黑格斯敦早期鐵路歷史的展品。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.roundhouse.org/ |title=Hagerstown Roundhouse Museum |accessdate=2020-09-23 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728025300/https://roundhouse.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===劇院和藝術===
馬里蘭州劇院位於本城內<ref name="Hag2" />，而提供晚宴劇場演出的華盛頓縣劇場亦位於本城內。社區劇場組波托馬克娛樂製造者（Potomac Playmakers）更以位於本城內的新學院劇院式宴會及會議中心作為總部。<ref>[http://www.herald-mail.com/?cmd=displaystory&story_id=210261&format=html Andrew Schotz, Downtown Hagerstown theater, banquet center takes center stage''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.herald-mail.com/?cmd=displaystory&story_id=210261&format=html |date=20130315171612 }}, The Herald-Mail. Published 18 November 2008. Retrieved 19 November 2008.</ref>

===節日和活動===
近年，黑格斯敦因經濟復蘇而舉辦多項活動。<ref name="Hag2" />Downtown Live!是其中一個活動，該活動內容主要為現場雷鬼音樂和搖滾音樂演出。<ref>[http://your4state.com/content/fulltext/?cid=35991 Jennifer Von Reuter, ''Downtown Live Band "Sister Hazel" Has Ties To Area'']{{dead link|date=六月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}, Your4State.com, Published Tuesday 21 October 2008, Retrieved 22 October 2008.</ref>本城在每年五月至六月期間都會舉辦名為「馬里蘭藍調巨星」（Maryland Blues Fest）的活動，邀請來自美國各地的藍調藝人演出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.blues-fest.org/ |title=Western Maryland Blues Fest |accessdate=2020-09-23 |archive-date=2018-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831041627/https://blues-fest.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>受歡迎的Augustoberfest活動則與黑格斯敦的德國文化有關。<ref name="Wesel1">{{cite web| title =Augustoberfest| work =City of Hagerstown, MD| date =| url =http://www.augustoberfest.org/history.html| accessdate =2007-07-07| archive-date =2014-07-02| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140702094346/http://www.augustoberfest.org/history.html| dead-url =no}}</ref>

[[展覽會場公園|展覽會場公園]]擁有不少康樂活動，其中包括黑格斯敦冰上及體育綜合運動場（Hagerstown Ice & Sports Complex）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hagerstownice.org/ |title=Hagerstown Ice & Sports Complex |accessdate=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2013-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719232127/http://www.hagerstownice.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和黑格斯敦西班牙節。<ref>[http://your4state.com/content/fulltext/?cid=13239 Kaitlin McCarthy, ''First Ever Hispanic Festival Takes Off In Washington County''] {{Wayback|url=http://your4state.com/content/fulltext/?cid=13239 |date=20080315184124 }}, Your4State.com, Published Sunday 16 September 2007, Retrieved November 2007.</ref><ref>[http://www.herald-mail.com/?cmd=displaystory&story_id=203998&format=html Joshua Bowman, ''Festival's growth reflects increase in local Hispanic population''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.herald-mail.com/?cmd=displaystory&story_id=203998&format=html |date=20130315171646 }}, Herald-Mail.com ONLINE, Published Sunday 20 September 2008, Retrieved 21 September 2008.</ref>

